{
  "stem": "11205.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And that they also-- like a miracle, I, I didn't have to go, but somehow I went back to the place where we lived.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the letter arrived that he applied.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we were very happy that he's going back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we didn't know where we are going and where he will be.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] we came to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And what happened, when he came, when he came back to Poland, he didn't have anybody, not, not a soul.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he, he went to our organization.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I don't remember, [NON-ENGLISH] or something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what organization, which were also that I'm-- that, you know, every organization that time was to go to, to Palestine, to Israel.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] so this organizations, they've been on the way like we did, to cross the border to go to, to Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he went to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Krakow, he went to, to the state [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] baths.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was in a cubicle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the next cubicle, he had talking to men about how the baths was in Stalinsk. and all the-- so when he finished, he came off.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, you were in Stalinsk?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And yes, and they found out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, did-- do you know us and my sister?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said, yes, that I stepped out in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They, they knew because it was very seldom somebody got family to take them, you know, to them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so he went there to, to Moniek's address, to Moniek's sister.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he found out that we are in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And just happened that this-- his organization was passing-- you know, [INAUDIBLE] was closer to the Czechoslovakian border.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they've been passing [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And suddenly, 1:00 in the morning, somebody knocked at the door.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I opened it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
